trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含集合<xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo"></xref>物件。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> class allows you to programmatically access and modify tag-prefix information stored in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>類別可讓您以程式設計方式存取及修改儲存在組態檔中的標記前置詞資訊。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>

trans-unit.source: Tag prefixes associate a "namespace" in ASP.NET with the assemblies and namespaces that must be included for custom controls and user controls to work properly.
trans-unit.target: 標記前置詞會在 ASP.NET 中的"namespace"關聯的組件和命名空間必須包含自訂控制項和使用者控制項才能正常運作。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> objects are stored as members of a TagPrefixCollection object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>物件會儲存為 TagPrefixCollection 物件的成員。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>

trans-unit.source: The TagPrefixCollection class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `controls` subsection of the `pages` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: TagPrefixCollection 類別可讓您以程式設計方式存取和修改`controls`小節的`pages`組態檔區段。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: The TagPrefixCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: TagPrefixCollection 建構函式不是直接從您的程式碼使用。

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: 它會呼叫 ASP.NET 組態系統。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection> class always contains an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection> type.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection>類別一定會包含執行個體<xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection>型別。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.Controls%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use this instance, rather than creating your own.
trans-unit.target: 這個執行個體，而不是建立您自己使用。

trans-unit.target: 新增<xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo"></xref>物件加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: The collection must not already contain a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo> object with the same property values.
trans-unit.target: 集合必須已經包含<xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>物件具有相同的屬性值。</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TagPrefixInfo>
